    "\n",
    "**Verdict:** ✅ Ideal for SaaS — permissive, commercial-friendly, no major restrictions.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### ⚠️ Model 2: meta-llama/Llama-2-7b-chat-hf\n",
