    "  - [x] Attribution required: must display "Built with Meta Llama 2"\n",
    "  - [x] Cannot use outputs to train other LLMs (competing model clause)\n",
    "  - [x] Cannot sub-license the model weights\n",
    "\n",
    "**Verdict:** ⚠️ Usable for most SaaS but with restrictions — check MAU cap and attribution clause before deployment.\n",
    "\"\"\"\n",
    "\n",
    "display(Markdown(license_checklist))"
   ]
  },
