    "---\n",
    "## 🌟 Exercise 4 : Local Readiness Audit"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Récupération automatique des specs système\n",
    "system = platform.system()\n",
    "release = platform.release()\n",
    "machine = platform.machine()\n",
    "\n",
    "# RAM\n",
    "if system == \"Darwin\":  # macOS\n",
    "    ram_bytes = int(subprocess.check_output([\"sysctl\", \"-n\", \"hw.memsize\"]).decode().strip())\n",
    "    ram_gb = ram_bytes / (1024 ** 3)\n",
    "    # Disk\n",
    "    df_output = subprocess.check_output([\"df\", \"-h\", \"/\"]).decode().strip().split(\"\\n\")\n",
    "    disk_parts = df_output[1].split()\n",
    "    disk_total = disk_parts[1]\n",
    "    disk_avail = disk_parts[3]\n",
    "else:  # Linux\n",
    "    mem_output = subprocess.check_output([\"free\", \"-h\"]).decode().strip().split(\"\\n\")\n",
    "    mem_parts = mem_output[1].split()\n",
    "    ram_gb = float(mem_parts[1].replace(\"G\", \"\").replace(\"Gi\", \"\"))\n",
    "    df_output = subprocess.check_output([\"df\", \"-h\", \"/\"]).decode().strip().split(\"\\n\")\n",
    "    disk_parts = df_output[1].split()\n",
    "    disk_total = disk_parts[1]\n",
    "    disk_avail = disk_parts[3]\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"OS          : {system} {release} ({machine})\")\n",
    "print(f\"RAM total   : {ram_gb:.1f} GB\")\n",
    "print(f\"Disk total  : {disk_total}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Disk free   : {disk_avail}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Audit table\n",
    "audit_data = {\n",
    "    \"Requirement\": [\"RAM (≥ 16 GB)\", \"Free Disk Space (≥ 40 GB)\", \"OS (Linux / WSL2 / macOS*)\"],\n",
    "    \"Your System Specs\": [\n",
    "        f\"{ram_gb:.1f} GB\",\n",
    "        f\"Free: {disk_avail} / Total: {disk_total}\",\n",
    "        f\"{system} {release}\"\n",
    "    ],\n",
    "    \"Meets Requirement?\": [\n",
    "        \"✅\" if ram_gb >= 16 else \"❌\",\n",
    "        \"✅\",  # update manually if needed\n",
    "        \"✅ (macOS supported by llama.cpp via Metal)\" if system == \"Darwin\" else \"✅\" if system == \"Linux\" else \"❌\"\n",
    "    ]\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "df_audit = pd.DataFrame(audit_data)\n",
    "display(df_audit)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Évaluation llama.cpp Readiness\n",
    "\n",
    "| Critère | Statut |\n",
    "|---------|--------|\n",
    "| CPU avec AVX/SSE (Intel/AMD) ou Apple Silicon | ✅ Apple Silicon supporte NEON + Metal GPU acceleration |\n",
    "| Compilateur C/C++ (clang/gcc) | ✅ Clang inclus avec Xcode Command Line Tools sur macOS |\n",
    "| cmake / make | ✅ Disponible via Homebrew (`brew install cmake`) |\n",
    "| Support GPU | ✅ Metal backend disponible sur macOS M1/M2/M3 |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Plan de mise à niveau\n",
    "\n",
    "Aucun upgrade critique nécessaire sur ce système. Pour exécuter un modèle 7B quantifié (4-bit GGUF) :\n",
    "- RAM ≥ 8 GB suffisant (modèle ~4 GB en mémoire)\n",
    "- Compiler llama.cpp avec Metal : `cmake -DLLAMA_METAL=on ..`\n",
    "- Télécharger un fichier `.gguf` depuis Hugging Face (ex: TheBloke/Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.2-GGUF)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 🌟 Exercise 5 : Benchmark-Based Model Explorer\n",
    "\n",
    "Source : [Open LLM Leaderboard – Hugging Face](https://huggingface.co/spaces/HuggingFaceH4/open_llm_leaderboard)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "benchmark_data = {\n",
    "    \"Model Name\": [\n",
    "        \"mistralai/Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.2\",\n",
    "        \"meta-llama/Meta-Llama-3-8B-Instruct\",\n",
    "        \"microsoft/phi-2\"\n",
    "    ],\n",
    "    \"Model URL\": [\n",
